  - Enhanced error handling with fallback empty array initialization
  - Added TypeScript interface for proper type safety instead of `any`
  - Improved debug logging for better troubleshooting
- **Files Fixed:**
  - `frontend/src/pages/Agent/components/AgentBuilder.tsx`
    - Fixed API response parsing (lines 125-135)
    - Added Array.isArray checks for map() calls (line 1426)
    - Added Array.isArray checks for find() calls (line 1439) 
    - Enhanced error handling with fallback arrays
